author: Jessica
title: ToysRUs: Cedarbrook Wood Gym Set Only $499.99 (Regularly $649.99) + More
text:
In the market for a new Swing Set? Through March 5th, head on over to ToysRUs.com where they are offering up a couple of nice deals on swing sets! As an idea, you can score this Big Backyard Cedarbrook Wood Gym Set for only $499.99 (regularly $649.99), but note that there is a $124.99 surcharge fee so choose free in-store pickup.
This set has a monkey bar with climbing ladder, extra deep high rail slide, lower picnic bench and table, a rock climbing wall, a glider for one or two passengers, 2 belt swings and a sandbox!
In addition, you can snag this Big Backyard Premium Collection Charleston Lodge Wood Swing Set for $1,299.99 (reg. $1,599.99) but there is a $199.99 shipping surcharge and this item is not available for store pickup. This set has a play clock, 12′ twist ‘n ride tube slide, a high-rail wave slide, a deluxe kitchen that includes a play stove and sink, a glider, two belt swings and a rock climbing wall.
